  24 Jun 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org> inn-2.4.3.ebuild:
  Filtering -Wl,--as-needed from LDFLAGS because it breaks the compilation.
  Fixes bug 182782. Thanks to Conrad Kostecki for spotting this!

